author: ehu
msg: Reduce required FS access calls for blame.
Note this clears the way for my fix for issue #2431.
* subversion/libsvn_client/blame.c
(file_rev_baton): Add new field for storing the cached filename for
generating temporary files.
(file_rev_handler): Use the new field in the file_rev_baton.
(svn_client_blame2): Initialize the new file_rev_baton.cached_tmp field.
